OL,3,CFormer Arsenal star to deny rape
OL,4,Ccharges, court told
OL,6,FFormer Arsenal footballer Thomas
OL,7,FPartey is set to deny two new
OL,8,Fallegations of rape, a court has heard.
OL,10,FThe midfielder was absent from the
OL,11,Fdock today for the first hearing at
OL,12,FWestminster Magistrates Court.
OL,14,FThe 32-year-old was charged last month
OL,15,Fwith two counts of raping a woman on a
OL,16,Fdate in December 2020.
OL,18,FThe footballer had been excused from
OL,19,Fthe hearing, but his lawyer, Emma
OL,20,FFenn, indicated he intends to plead
OL,21,Fnot guilty to both charges.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
