OL,3,CFormer Arsenal star to deny rape
OL,4,Ccharges, court told
OL,6,FPartey was charged last year with five
OL,7,Fcounts of rape against two women and
OL,8,Fsexual assault against a third alleged
OL,9,Fvictim, following a Metropolitan
OL,10,FPolice investigation.
OL,12,FHe has already entered not guilty
OL,13,Fpleas to all of those allegations,
OL,14,Fwhich date back to 2021 and 2022, and
OL,15,Fis due to face trial at Southwark
OL,16,FCrown Court in November.
OL,18,FThe court heard that the two new
OL,19,Fallegations of rape came to light
OL,20,Fafter the first set of charges had
OL,21,Fbeen revealed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
