OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773666673
OL,3,CFormer Arsenal star to deny rape
OL,4,Ccharges, court told
OL,6,FPartey was released on bail, with the
OL,7,Fcondition that he does not contact the
OL,8,Falleged victim.
OL,10,FThe footballer, who previously lived
OL,11,Fin Potters Bar in Hertfordshire,
OL,12,Fjoined Arsenal from Atletico Madrid in
OL,13,F2020 in a transfer worth around #45
OL,14,Fmillion, before he left the club in
OL,15,FJune last year.
OL,17,FPartey is expected to attend the next
OL,18,Fcourt hearing in April.
